data.description: Welcome to your new home!  This updated Four Bedroom and Three Bathroom Colonial is located on private 3 acre setting. Welcoming, spacious first floor with hardwoods in living room, foyer & dining room with bay window. Family room has fireplace with new mantel & hardwoods. Updated kitchen w/custom cabinets, gas stove, stainless steel appliances, center island & dining area. Laundry room w/washer, dryer & cabinets. First floor bathroom. Home Office with skylight, recessed lighting & its own separate entrance. Second floor has primary bedroom with double closets & private updated bathroom w/tiled shower. Three additional bedrooms with closets.  Updated main bathroom with double sinks, tiled tub & shower. Basement with finished bonus room, great for play room or media room. Two Car Garage. Forced Air Gas Heat. Gas cooking. Some updated windows. Large yard ~ great for dog lovers & garden beds for gardeners. Direct access to aqueduct trail. Close to major highways for commuting. A must see!
